N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 647.16 - Costs and fees

State Regulations

Any person filing a notice of appeal shall pay to the
docket clerk a filing fee as the board shall set, in postal money order, certified or bank check, or attorney's check. Notes
